Class BTOapplication

java.lang.Object
bto.model.BTOapplication
public class BTOapplication extends Object
BTO application that holds all the information and methods for an Applicant's application Able to display application details: User ID, Project ID, Unit type, Application Status, Last Update Status Creates a BTO application for Applicant
